WEBVTT

00:01:30.537 --> 00:01:32.873
Do not be afraid to say, "Yes."

00:01:33.777 --> 00:01:36.561
Start by being a better listener.

00:01:37.214 --> 00:01:40.161
Start by being better
at walking down the street.

00:01:40.547 --> 00:01:41.922
See people.

00:01:41.946 --> 00:01:43.422
Say, "Hello."

00:01:43.446 --> 00:01:46.557
Ask how they are doing
and listen to what they say.

00:01:47.333 --> 00:01:49.559
Start by being a better friend,

00:01:49.583 --> 00:01:52.443
a better parent,
a better child to your parents;

00:01:52.467 --> 00:01:55.541
a better sibling, a better lover,
a better partner.

00:01:55.922 --> 00:01:58.789
Start by being a better neighbor.

00:01:58.813 --> 00:02:02.155
Meet someone you do not know,
and get to know them.